data.description: Below market value!!! Hurry this is an incredible opportunity! Nestled within the picturesque landscape of Woodstock's esteemed Eagle Watch subdivision, this 4-bedroom, 3.5-bathroom sanctuary at 1091 Longwood Drive is an embodiment of refined elegance and comfort just 150 yards to Lake Allatoona! A seamless fusion of modern sophistication and timeless Charleston charm, this residence presents an unparalleled living experience.    Step inside and be greeted by the allure of a home that truly captivates. The main level boasts an airy ambiance courtesy of its impressive 12-foot ceilings, creating a sense of openness and grandeur. The living room with a wood burning or gas fireplace, dining room, and an adaptable office/flex space provide versatile options for personalized use, catering effortlessly to both relaxation and productivity.    Upstairs, discover a haven of tranquility with three bedrooms with breathtaking treeline views in the distance that will stiop you instantly in your tour. With two full baths, convenience and privacy are seamlessly integrated into the design.    The allure doesn't end there. A recently remodeled basement awaits, showcasing a thoughtfully designed bar, an additional bedroom, and a full bathroom, perfect for accommodating guests or indulging in leisurely pursuits. Revel in the upscale hardwoods that grace the main and upper levels, exuding a timeless luster and elegance that speaks to the meticulous attention to detail throughout.     Outside, a private yard beckons, offering a serene escape for outdoor gatherings and quiet moments of reflection. Two decks provide the perfect setting for savoring the surrounding natural beauty, while the proximity to the mesmerizing Lake Allatoona, merely 150 yards away, ensures a lifestyle enriched by nature's splendid offerings.    As you approach the property, the front facade captures your gaze with its stunning redesign, boasting custom features such as a welcoming porch adorned with stately stone pillars, inviting recessed lighting, and the gentle embrace of dual ceiling fans, ensuring a seamless blend of functionality and style.    Located at the peaceful end of Longwood Drive, the home enjoys the tranquility of its surroundings, culminating in a serene cul-de-sac that promises a peaceful retreat from the bustle of everyday life. Envision the harmonious blend of modern convenience, traditional allure, and natural beauty that this home effortlessly embodies, offering a truly unmatched living experience in the heart of Woodstock's most sought-after locale.  This home offers a newer HVAC. You will not want to wait on this one!!!   Eagle Watch offers resort like amentities with 3 pools, pickleball,12 tennis courts, two playgrounds, dog park and an incredible social committee!
